    },
    {
      "audio": 14,
      "lines": [
        {
          "ja": "そのまんまなんですね",
          "en": "It's exactly as it is."
        },
        {
          "ja": "あの　もしかして 雑誌とかに載ってないですか？",
          "en": "Um, by any chance, is it featured in magazines or anything like that?"
